{"tid":1318083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[軍政府做野] 大專生比親軍政府廢老打 原告變被告以”普通襲擊”拘捕","createTime":"2019-07-15T01:07:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T01:30:31.000Z","uid":51620,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"89bd4fb1aa75475406138a28689998623eada853","tid":1318083,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T01:07:15.000Z","msg":"建制派議員何君堯上月30日在金鐘添馬公園發起撐警集會，有戴口罩市民無端被撐警人士毆打。今年20歲的大專生鄧先生向《蘋果》投訴指，當日因身體不適戴上口罩，路過海富天橋其間突遭大批撐警人士上前圍毆，被熊抱拉扯至倒地仍被「起飛腳」施襲，但警方卻未有拘捕任何施襲者，反以「普通襲擊」罪拘捕他，他批評警方做法偏頗，撐警人士尤如獲「免死金牌」，「只要我話我支持警察，就咩事都唔使俾人拉」。<br />\n<br />\n鄧先生稱，當日傍晚約5時與友人欲前往添馬公園，「我諗住觀察吓，見佢哋話﹙撐警集會﹚聲勢好浩大㗎嘛&hellip;&hellip;想睇吓佢哋有冇可能派吓錢」，他指自己不屬任何政黨成員，事發當日穿淺白色有圖案恤衫、無穿黑衣，手上只持雨傘，未帶任何示威標語及叫口號，因為身體不適而戴上口罩，其同伴亦穿白衣，沒料到未行至公園，在海富天橋突遭一名穿藍衣男士上前扯走其口罩，及後再被一班相信是出席撐警集會的男女圍毆約3分鐘，其間有人上前熊抱拉扯令他倒地，有人在他倒地後施以腳踢，亦有人上前狂抓其頭髮，令他手腳受傷，背包肩帶被扯爛，「我諗住佢哋好和平，但估唔到佢哋咁暴力，見到人戴口罩，就群情洶湧咁樣又鬧、又打、又搶、又扯咁樣。」<br />\n<br />\n他指警方接報到場後分隔他與施襲者，並在他登上警車後指控他以雨傘襲擊在場一名男子，認為難以置信，「我無郁過手打佢哋，我被人（出手）鎖住手腳，點樣打人？」他稱因遇襲受傷，曾要求召喚救護車但遭警方拒絕，指要待他到中區警署落口供後才驗傷，結果他由當日5時多被警方拘捕後，翌日（7月1日）上午約7時才可以500元保釋，並要在7月中到警署報到。<br />\n<br />\n鄧先生指，除對警方將他由原告變被告的處理手法感到驚訝，「令我最憤怒，係我喺警署聽到打我嗰幾個人﹙返警署落口供﹚，變咗做所謂受害者同證人」，他認為即使一般毆鬥，警方都應拘捕全部施襲者，「何況我無還手，但反而捉我返去，我係被人打嗰個，反而變咗做被告」。他批評警方做法偏頗，令撐警人士如獲「免死金牌」，積極考慮就警方今次處理手法向警察投訴課及監警會投訴。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》曾就鄧先生的投訴向警方查詢，包括為何未有拘捕施襲者，警方只回覆指，當日下午於海富天橋發現一名56歲姓王男子與一名20歲姓鄧男子因瑣事問題爭執，王男聲稱被鄧男以雨傘襲擊，警方接報到場後，鄧姓本地男子涉嫌普通襲擊被捕，現已獲准保釋候查，7月中再向警方報到，案件由中區警區重案組跟進調查，始終未有解釋為何不拘捕施襲者。<br />\n<br />\n據羅冠聰facebook上載的片段，當時鄧先生在橋上被幾名男士拉扯，甚至按在地上，未有還手；雖然短片未有紀錄雙方相遇一刻，工黨立法會議員張超雄看過片段後也指，鄧先生在片中明顯遇襲，警方若無拘捕施襲者，反映警方十分偏袒，「似乎佢哋（警方）已經有一個立場，撐警嘅就無錯，被撐警人士襲擊嘅人反而有錯，呢個係完全不能接受，因為警隊應該政治中立，咁樣係好有問題」。他指如鄧先生所言屬實，警方應一併拘捕施襲者。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190715&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59816161\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190715%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59816161&d=MD3su0BfWHBnm8Iidd6ZKZS3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=c8dd2e0d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190715%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59816161&h=cb762922\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190715&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59816161</a>"},{"pid":"c60ed404ea8e5e5e47b6196ab5efa96f7e1ac5bc","tid":1318083,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T01:08:32.000Z","msg":"［純紓發］我們缺乏了什麼？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1316095\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1316095</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"35934dce9890ce3c990765d5856de071493e4f75","tid":1318083,"uid":5205,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T01:09:31.000Z","msg":"請律師幫佢手"},{"pid":"db5369afac5aead124a63157e8b9edb7ea6061b4","tid":1318083,"uid":51620,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"35934dce9890ce3c990765d5856de071493e4f75","tid":1318083,"uid":5205,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T01:09:31.000Z","msg":"請律師幫佢手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T01:12:18.000Z","msg":"而家就係考驗司法獨立嘅時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2a07bf3d524d561493450e6ebd2b1a4b6072e62","tid":1318083,"uid":179967,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"35934dce9890ce3c990765d5856de071493e4f75","tid":1318083,"uid":5205,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T01:09:31.000Z","msg":"請律師幫佢手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T01:12:43.000Z","msg":"律師幫條柒<br />\n依家好明顯就係見人就拉 佢都唔望告得你入純粹玩鳩你+無罪藍絲<br />\n請律師仲衰 無啦啦唔見錢?"},{"pid":"993be7709e617220fdaf3dc12888f0a2878e3b68","tid":1318083,"uid":48057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T01:14:51.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"02d393c8932b0a842c25259158fdcc413d33d61c","tid":1318083,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T01:15:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"590171f6effd3d299692de0db2757c73cb32d27e","tid":1318083,"uid":263336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T01:27:21.000Z","msg":"陽光執法"},{"pid":"bd37cc6549a44b8638dea18b6a38b1ff43196d9f","tid":1318083,"uid":24853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T01:32:49.000Z","msg":"搵6c"},{"pid":"82b50fb0f5a704ff7045d3fc6600a0aa0d838d1f","tid":1318083,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T01:34:13.000Z","msg":"狗狗抵做過街老鼠"},{"pid":"25c1c9c530f0eca2c846a852522bef6adf3a306e","tid":1318083,"uid":171313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T01:38:58.000Z","msg":"原告變被告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港悲哀"},{"pid":"aff6f85aeec7f0e4b6552993564f4e1876cfd096","tid":1318083,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T01:39:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efe3b2cacc59146160ab2b98bdf8f03681036651","tid":1318083,"uid":84581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T01:39:07.000Z","msg":"Parasite.<br />\n成班廢佬都係社會寄生蟲"},{"pid":"6347cb630154ea58cb9329d4978988295e6c4f07","tid":1318083,"uid":158090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T01:40:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3db264575f959666d4e3d3e242025c53b2624d75","tid":1318083,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T01:43:18.000Z","msg":"有冇民間法援"},{"pid":"a9639e9435ce9a11756c21bea3dfcef444bef321","tid":1318083,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T01:43:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f6686865099cf5b6e5788fbcb9b3e2a881fad868","tid":1318083,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9639e9435ce9a11756c21bea3dfcef444bef321","tid":1318083,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35934dce9890ce3c990765d5856de071493e4f75","tid":1318083,"uid":5205,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T01:09:31.000Z","msg":"請律師幫佢手"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T01:43:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:27:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0960ea9e8fe9bf1fcd52c4ffc2a761c96e57da9b","tid":1318083,"uid":28451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:29:46.000Z","msg":"明白事理果啲其實都明晒，剩低都係弱智廢老<br />\n講道理嘅文宣差唔多已到盡頭，我覺得可以用無賴文宣<br />\n以子之矛攻子之盾，用返佢地個邏輯講<br />\n除左做文宣本身之外，仲可以提供答案，用黎回應藍絲親戚<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無賴文宣，正式啟動</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n學藍絲話齋，如果係外國，個警察死撚左喇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1316434\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1316434</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"808e00c7195143c6999583df3e4d0bce6e9ea706","tid":1318083,"uid":271123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:30:14.000Z","msg":"我係荃灣都比人屈左劑，而家仲保釋期間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07b893157d3c9def2e915deab6faa727a98f4247","tid":1318083,"uid":265761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:30:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1318293/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1318293/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">a.</span></strong> 口罩同帽戴得耐會熱所以就會除. 除完想洗手, 所以去洗手間除就最方便.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">b.</span></strong> 香港人羊群心理鍾意跟大隊.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">c.</span></strong> 戴口罩同除口罩可以係兩個人, 所以成日話冇樣唔好亂J.<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">d.</span></strong> 香港法律講求&quot;無合理疑點.&quot;<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>e.</strong></span> 我無野講 我唔解鎖 我要搵律師<br />\n<br />\n代人宣傳:<br />\n&quot;其實警方<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">認人</span></strong>係法律上有<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>好嚴謹</strong></span>既要求，可以自己查下Turnbull guideline，就算你有無同99有身體接觸都好，其實<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>你有頭盔同口罩可以當係環境証供</strong></span>之一，所以未必話到嗰個係你，但如果<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>你搵個無police睇到既地掉左帽同除左口罩再融入人群，係更加好難指証你</strong></span>。<br />\n如果你無同police對抽，多數告你參與非法集結，而<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>你如果有戴口罩，更加認唔到你，官冇可能係無合理疑點下話個個係你</strong></span>。&quot;"},{"pid":"48a180d4d5733f40b1031ed5f9911b6d5b5f6e7b","tid":1318083,"uid":258492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:33:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f629ea41e6b39f66b639ab6b50d6b093a3778243","tid":1318083,"uid":159920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:35:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1864fe3bc5c4ffb49031e3d303e511816751fc12","tid":1318083,"uid":81652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:38:04.000Z","msg":"所以話比人打老虎蟹都還拖先，反正還唔還拖都比人告"},{"pid":"31b05d17fb709c6b2158cb96cd2e8847a587e184","tid":1318083,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T01:30:31.000Z","msg":"要推<br />\n依家香港撐警做咩都得"}]}